data.text:
SAYA is world-class athlete management and the leading sports organization started by our CEO Talha Rehmani in 2014. Saya represents 70% of the Pakistan National Team including the top-ranked athletes like Babar Azam ( ICC World No 1 batter in ODIs), Muhammad Rizwan (ICC World No 1 WK/batter in T20I), Shaheen Shah Afridi, Rassie van der Dussen, Michael Rippon, Sandeep Lamichhane, etc. Moreover, most of our athletes participate in well-renowned international leagues. We have an amazingly proficient and dedicated cadre working in top-class leagues around the globe and have the privilege of creating and designing premier sports properties and elevating them to new heights.

Through the rise of our new philanthropic startups and partnering with other companies striving to work for human welfare, we have always endeavored to give back to society and bring a positive impact.

Our mission is very simple; providing the deprived a privilege to represent the best and create a legacy.
